<br>
I'm level 60 now, and have a staff of elemental mastery: water. Focussed, I find the pet can tank some things pretty well. I can use it to pet mezz many mobs in Sebilis for example, and generally will not lost the pet (without healing even). This pet is basiclly about doing damage, not taking it. Unfocussed it's better damage than the other pets, but cannot reallly take damage for too long. But get the staff and the pet can not only dish it out better than any of the other pets, it can even take damage fairly well (and heals pretty quick it seems).<br>
<br>
Water has always been my favorite pet though, so I am biased =).<br>
